Package edu.cmu.sei.arche.ui.dialog

Class Summary
FunctionDialog Dialog box where the user can add a new function or edit an existing one.
FunctionRespMappingDialog Dialog box where the user can add a new function-responsibility mapping or edit an existing one.
QuestionToUserDialog Dialog box used to show a question to the user and send the answer provided by him to the core.
RelationshipDialog Dialog box where the user can add a new Relationship or edit an existing one.
ResponsibilityDialog Dialog box where the user can add a new responsibility or edit an existing one.
ScenarioDialog Scenario dialog box used to add and edit one scenario at a time.
ScenarioRespMappingDialog Dialog box where the user can add a new scenario-responsibility mapping or edit an existing one.
